  "notes": "Plex documents broad Xbox Direct Play support across ASF, AVI, MOV, MP4, MPEG, MPEGTS/TS, MKV, and WMV, plus 4K support for compatible MP4/MKV HEVC, MPEG4, and VP9 files. DTS and TrueHD are passthrough-only conditions: Xbox system passthrough must be enabled, the connected AVR/TV must support the codec, and Plex must be fully Direct Playing rather than Direct Streaming or transcoding.",
